{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01LiDaR3RpA4oqK9PC49LWUB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01NQzVCf2cUFq2rvWoizYVVQ","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/run_detail.html","old_string":"    var logContent = document.getElementById('log-content');\n    var logViewer = document.getElementById('log-viewer');\n    var logStatus = document.getElementById('log-status');\n    var loadEarlierBtn = document.getElementById('load-earlier-btn');\n    var loadEarlierCount = document.getElementById('load-earlier-count');\n    var skippedLines = 0;\n\n    function appendLogLine(line) {\n        var span = document.createElement('span');\n        span.className = 'log-line log-type-' + (line.type || 'script');\n        span.textContent = '[' + line.timestamp + '] [' + line.type + '] ' + line.content + '\\n';\n\n        // Check scroll position BEFORE appending to avoid race conditions\n        // with the scroll event listener approach.\n        var savedScrollTop = logViewer.scrollTop;\n        var atBottom = logViewer.scrollHeight - savedScrollTop - logViewer.clientHeight < 40;\n\n        logContent.appendChild(span);\n\n        if (atBottom) {\n            logViewer.scrollTop = logViewer.scrollHeight;\n        } else {\n            // Restore scroll position in case the DOM mutation shifted it\n            logViewer.scrollTop = savedScrollTop;\n        }\n    }","new_string":"    var logContent = document.getElementById('log-content');\n    var logViewer = document.getElementById('log-viewer');\n    var logStatus = document.getElementById('log-status');\n    var loadEarlierBtn = document.getElementById('load-earlier-btn');\n    var loadEarlierCount = document.getElementById('load-earlier-count');\n    var skippedLines = 0;\n\n    // Per-step log line buffers: stepName -> [line, ...]\n    var stepLogBuffers = {};\n\n    function appendToElement(container, pre, line) {\n        var span = document.createElement('span');\n        span.className = 'log-line log-type-' + (line.type || 'script');\n        span.textContent = '[' + line.timestamp + '] [' + line.type + '] ' + line.content + '\\n';\n\n        var savedScrollTop = container.scrollTop;\n        var atBottom = container.scrollHeight - savedScrollTop - container.clientHeight < 40;\n\n        pre.appendChild(span);\n\n        if (atBottom) {\n            container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;\n        } else {\n            container.scrollTop = savedScrollTop;\n        }\n    }\n\n    function appendLogLine(line) {\n        appendToElement(logViewer, logContent, line);\n\n        // Buffer and route to per-step accordion\n        if (line.step_name) {\n            if (!stepLogBuffers[line.step_name]) {\n                stepLogBuffers[line.step_name] = [];\n            }\n            stepLogBuffers[line.step_name].push(line);\n\n            // If the step's accordion pre is visible, append live\n            var pres = document.querySelectorAll('.step-output[data-step=\"' + line.step_name + '\"]');\n            for (var i = 0; i < pres.length; i++) {\n                var pre = pres[i];\n                var viewer = pre.closest('.step-log-viewer');\n                if (viewer && pre.closest('.output-row').style.display !== 'none') {\n                    appendToElement(viewer, pre, line);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":434,"cache_read_input_tokens":64959,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":434},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ab06b6b4-e6b6-4d23-a886-0560ffd72710","uuid":"a124f028-f77f-4286-a67f-3e3f6bf842b0"}
